name: Maera - The Baker
description:
Piece Of Cake collectible Esoteric cards starring Goddesses and Daemons.

Maera the Baker is one of the few creatures in the Tezos Blockchain that wants you well. You can't find her though, you'll cross her path whenever you hold enough Tezos. She will offer you to manage your fund. If you accept, you may earn extra tezos in the long term ! 

Be careful of the Corrupted Maera though, this one is never far away…
